        <title>Sundance 2011: A Family Portrait in Black and White/The Green Wave</title>
        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/typepad/GoodyErin/blog/~3/XShbdHg3AbQ/sundance-a-family-.html" />
